snippet.description:
CHILDREN'S MUSEUM Family Fun Trip Kids Pretend Play Indoor & Outdoor Play Area with Ryan ToysReview! Ryan's family had a family fun trip to kids indoor play area and outdoor water fun with lots of Children Activities filled with learning toys for Kids and pretend food.  Kids can interactive play and pretend to a doctor or dentist or pretend play farming. There's even kid size shopping trip to grocery store for pretend food like apple. THere's also a outdoor playground with slides!nThere's also play sand for kids in giant sandbox, and kids can pretend go fishing, ride on cars like superman and be a chef! Great Indoor Play Center for fun learning experiences for children! Fun Kids Video for children who loves learning and playing with toys at the same time!

snippet.title: New Normal Outdoor Play | Where to go? What to do?
snippet.description:
Before anything else, please subscribe to our vlog, click this link: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmzFhoP0hC5lV3Vw1YpOX2A?view_as=subscriber

Being indoors for 7 months has taken a toll on us. So after researching on where to go and all of the safety protocols, we finally decided to have some family outdoor time. This is now the new normal for outdoor play. Sharing some tips for other parents out there. 

But still no meeting up with friends or household-to-household visits for us :)

Follow us on:
Instagram: http://instagram.com/alfieangelica
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DespiSquad
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/alfieangelica

Shot by Marvin
Edited by me

snippet.title: Brian Johnson: Boston - 8 Months In
snippet.description:
In this session, President of Mass MEDIC Brian Johnson discusses the virtual pivot that the organization has orchestrated in response to the pandemic during the course of 2020.

Want to see more? SUBSCRIBE to watch the latest podcasts: https://bit.ly/2UgRa2S

Connect with Joe: 
LINKEDIN: https://www.linkedin.com/in/joemullings
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/joemullings
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/joemullings
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/joemullings

WEBSITE: https://www.joemullings.com

About Joe:
Chairman & CEO of TMG Companies – A world leader in building companies and careers in the medtech industry.

Executive Producer and Host of True Future TV – Join us behind the scenes as we expose cutting edge medical technology and dive into the minds of creators.

Founder & CEO of DragonFly Stories – A production company specializing in a media-first approach to building a brand and maintaining a positive reputation.
 
I’m Joe Mullings, I’ve been building companies and careers for over three decades with The Mullings Group. We are the leading firm in the medical device industry and have worked with some of the greatest minds in the world. In light of the current challenges facing the world, I have landed in the forefront of the conversation in pursuit of spreading useful knowledge and resources.
 
Stay tuned as I take you behind the scenes and provide access to the manufacturers and caregivers who are on the front line of this global pandemic. COVID-19 is far from over. My goal is to be your gateway for information and the central resource of trusted and reliable sources.
 
“Be unreasonably relentless on a daily basis & powerfully patient for the long term play” – Joe Mullings  
 
See you on the other side.

snippet.title: Epic Beach Homes
snippet.description: The ocean is everywhere in and around these Epic Beach Homes.  With two story windows, outdoor showers and indoor rivers, these owners make the most of their breathtaking views and water's edge locations while fending off floods and hurricanes.

snippet.title: Cahill: U.S. Marshal
snippet.description: John Wayne stars as Cahill, the last man you want to see--and the last man you ever will, unless you've robbed a bank and he happens to be your father--in this Western about a rugged U.S. marshal who discovers that his two neglected sons are involved in the bank robbery he is investigating.
